casebody.data:
No. 10-224. National Meat Association, Petitioner v. Kamala D. Harris, Attorney General of California, et al. 564 U.S. 1036, 131 S. Ct. 3083,

180 L. Ed. 2d 884,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 4961. June 27, 2011.

Motion of American Association of Swine Veterinarians, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit granted.

Same case below, 599 F.3d 1093.
